  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of element managed by the collection.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    craterdog.core.Composite<Sequence<E>>, craterdog.core.Sequential<E>, java.lang.Comparable<Sequence<E>>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OrderedCollection, SortableCollection

    public abstract class OpenCollection<E>
extends Collection<E>
    This abstract class implements a collection that allows its internal structure to be directly manipulated.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
